---
title: Chicken Risotto with Saffron and Gremolata
description: Authentic, comforting, and simple enough to rustle up in 35 minutes, this chicken and saffron risotto will bring a little bit of low-key luxury to your dinner time routine. To take flavours to the next level, we’ve topped it with oven roasted tomatoes and an authentic gremolata, a popular Italian garnish which will give a lovely crunchy texture to this deliciously creamy dish.
